}
```

Or with the Stream API by abusing `Map.Entry` to build the inverse:

```
final Map&lt;String, List&lt;Integer&gt;&gt; target = source.entrySet()
  .stream()
  .flatMap(e -&gt; e.getValue().stream().map(s -&gt; Map.entry(s, e.getKey()))
